---
title: Mild Indian Chicken & Veggie Couscous with Slivered Almonds & Pumpkin Seeds
description: They say variety is the spice of life, so we’ve combined succulent chicken and roasted cauliflower with North Indian
flavours for the ultimate meal that’s sure to please! Just add some sweet currants for an explosion of colour and
flavour.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
